","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","padding_bottom":0}},"accordion_QgCAgY":{"type":"accordion","settings":{"style":"collapsible","show_description":false,"show_read_more":true,"default_open":false,"heading":"Make It Yours, Without the Extra Fees","heading_font_size":"body-medium","text":"<p>At Solarii, customization shouldn't cost a fortune. We’ve waived all labor fees—you only pay for premium materials.<\/p><p><strong>✨ What’s FREE (On the House):<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Custom Sizing:<\/strong> Any size, including <strong>1\/4 sizes<\/strong>.<\/li><li><strong>Personalization:<\/strong> Free engraving (Name, Date, or Message).<\/li><li><strong>Design Tweaks:<\/strong> Adjust stone size or styling.<\/li><li><strong>Gold Tone:<\/strong> Choose Yellow, Rose, or White Gold plating at no extra cost.<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>💎 Premium Upgrades (At Material Cost):<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Solid Gold:<\/strong> Upgrade to 10K, 14K, 18K, or 24K Gold.<\/li><li><strong>Stone Upgrade:<\/strong> Switch to premium Moissanite.<\/li><\/ul><p>👉 <strong>Ready to start?<\/strong> Email us at service@solariijewelry.com.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","show_icon":false,"icon_name":"icon-award","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"","padding_bottom":8}},"icon_1":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-notes","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/16-1.png","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454","text":"<p>Free returns within 30 days.<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","width":"quarter","padding_bottom":16}},"icon_663HJF":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-award","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/111_0e8b32a0-ddfc-48d4-883e-76c70a175052.png","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454","text":"<p>Lifetime warranty<\/p>","text_font_size":"body-medium","width":"quarter","padding_bottom":16}},"icon_2":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-truck","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/16-2.png","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#545454","text"